    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835240/extras/35edd94eea8969678108f7dc66542ff1.avif?t=1748710100\" width=600 height=248 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835240/extras/b00a3723cd93f0e4568f5eb690c6c92c.webp?t=1748710100\" width=600 height=55 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835240/extras/dbde5c93fcbaab3bbc16e3a67581713e.poster.avif?t=1748710100\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835240/extras/dbde5c93fcbaab3bbc16e3a67581713e.webm?t=1748710100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835240/extras/dbde5c93fcbaab3bbc16e3a67581713e.mp4?t=1748710100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Spiritfall</strong> 将紧凑的平台格斗、流畅移动和Roguelite机制融为一体！在危险的土地上跋涉，在随机生成的地图上获取多种多样的神力，用致命的连击击退成群的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835240/extras/c3049bb1b207552aba77dd526c045ad1.webp?t=1748710100\" width=600 height=55 /></span><br><br>神圣之灵会提供强大赐福，增强你的战斗能力。发掘最喜欢的能力，尝试不同的搭配。游戏中有150+赐福可供选择，你可以尝试各种流派，找到最适合自己的风格与思路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835240/extras/dbac85f9b125e20f86bf715110ea052f.webp?t=1748710100\" width=600 height=55 /></span><br>死亡只是一时挫折。在圣所苏醒后，你将变得更加强大，并继续冒险。使用收集到的资源升级技能，解锁独特能力，唤醒拥有独特招式的强力武器。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835240/extras/dd6807828928faa0ed0333c6c5fdc652.webp?t=1748710100\" width=600 height=55 /></span><br>衷心感谢参加了抢先体验版本的玩家社群！在Spiritfall的开发过程中，你们提供了非常宝贵的反馈意见，帮助游戏成长到了今天。我们邀请你继续共同塑造世界。欢迎加入Discord和其他玩家交流，也欢迎订阅我们的报纸以获得游戏的最新消息。",
